<title>Request API</title>
<p>Hello, This is an api for different needs</p>
<p>1. To echo something, write: <a href="https://request-kama.herokuapp.com/?echo=something">https://request-kama.herokuapp.com/?echo=something</a></p>
<p>2. To download any file from any server write: <a href="https://request-kama.herokuapp.com/?download=/file.txt">https://request-kama.herokuapp.com/?download=http://site/where/is/any/file/you/want/to/download.it</a></p>
<p>3. To save a txt file with contents write: <a href="https://request-kama.herokuapp.com/?save=somecontext">https://request-kama.herokuapp.com/?save=somecontext</a></p>
